Angel Smith, Big Brother Naija’s star, has taken to Twitter to celebrate some of her big wins at the age of 21. She claims that from being suicidal to owning a house, a car, and saving millions. “Don’t Get Married Or Have Kids If You Are Broke”- Ifu Ennada BBNaija Star Tochi Proposes To US-based Girlfriend Chioma… Read what she wrote below, ”I don’t acknowledge my progress enough, so today I just want to say that I have done so much for myself at 21. I’ve gotten a house, bought a car, saved millions, cried, laughed, fallen down just to get back up again. I acknowledge myself and acknowledge how far I’ve come. ”From being suicidal and not having a clear vision of what I wanted for life to being here? Where everything is getting clearer? Yeah, I’m doing great.”